  asymmetric_flow: 'Text containers positioned asymmetrically: standort in TOP-RIGHT
    corner (70% from left, 5% from top), headline/subline positioned more centrally
    and higher up (30-35% from left, 10-22% from top), stellentitel positioned between
    subline and CTA (50% from left, 50% from top), CTA positioned further right in
    bottom-right (70% from left, 85% from top) creating balanced asymmetric composition'
  background_motiv_handling: Full canvas background image with visible white text
    containers arranged asymmetrically
  container_behavior: Container size scales inversely with layout composition slider
    - smaller containers = more background visible (inverse logic)
  image_positioning: Background image covers full canvas (0,0 to 1080,1080), no cropping
    or borders
  layout_behavior: Text containers are arranged asymmetrically with standort positioned
    in TOP-RIGHT corner (70% from left, 5% from top), headline and subline positioned
    more centrally and higher up (30-35% from left, 10-22% from top), stellentitel
    positioned between subline and CTA (50% from left, 50% from top), CTA positioned
    further right in bottom-right (70% from left, 85% from top), container size varies
    inversely with slider, background image always visible
  negative_prompts: text rendering, readable text, visible text, text overlay, text
    on image
  scene_description: Professional recruitment creative with asymmetric text containers
    overlaid on background image
  separate_layers: true
  style_guidelines: Modern, clean design with professional typography, visible white
    containers with shadows, corporate color scheme
  text_positioning: 'All text elements in visible white containers with rounded corners,
    subtle shadows, and asymmetric positioning creating dynamic composition. CRITICAL:
    standort must be positioned in TOP-RIGHT corner, NOT top-left'
  visual_structure: Background image fills entire canvas, asymmetric arrangement of
    visible white text containers
